strings:
<voice_0x01000C69><se_high>Emma: Are you feeling all right, Your Majesty?
It's me. Emma, the maid.

<voice_0x01000C6A><se_high>Emma: I see you haven't eaten any of the lunch I brought you, Your Majesty. I'll be sure to
bring you your favourite for supper...

<voice_0x01000C6C><se_high>Emma: Please, Your Majesty. Please answer me.
I just want to make sure you're all right.

<voice_0x01000C6D><se_high>Emma: ...Very well.
I'll leave you in peace.
Excuse me.
